    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are done, add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the pot and give everything a good shake up</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
