    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy basa</strong> with the <strong>buttery potatoes</strong> and a handful of <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> to the side with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Spoon the <strong>sauce vierge</strong> over the crispy fish and drizzle the salad with a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
